Class QueueService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.shephertz.app42.paas.sdk.android.App42Service
      • com.shephertz.app42.paas.sdk.android.message.QueueService

  • public class QueueService
extends App42Service
    Manages Asynchronous queues. Allows to create, delete, purge messages, view pending messages and get all messages
